      "text": "ハイヒールを履いて頭に本を乗せ、落とさないように\n歩くことで、美しい姿勢で歩く技術を身につけます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll put books on my head while wearing high heels and try to walk without dropping them.\nBy doing so‚ I can develop the skill to walk with a beautiful posture.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
